33
00:01:24,459 --> 00:01:28,858
Enable strict mode - All strict options in tsconfig.json.

34
00:01:28,858 --> 00:01:32,716
Prefer interfaces - For object types that may be extended.

35
00:01:32,716 --> 00:01:36,802
Use const assertions - For literal types and immutability.

36
00:01:36,802 --> 00:01:40,637
Discriminated unions - For handling multiple related types.

37
00:01:40,637 --> 00:01:44,387
Avoid any - Use unknown with type guards instead.

38
00:01:44,387 --> 00:01:47,884
Runtime validation - Use Zod for external data.

39
00:01:47,884 --> 00:01:50,733
Result types - For explicit error handling.

40
00:01:50,733 --> 00:01:54,891
Generic constraints - Make functions type-safe and reusable.

